{
  "stem": "9091.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and I knew that is the only way that I can help somehow, you know, for ours-- for us, for my brother, and me.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so I kept on doing it, and quite a while, till one day he found-- he found me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He saw me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he almost killed me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So after that, we couldn't stay anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because it was-- we were starving there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There is another incident that I want to mention.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Before we even reached Samarkand, on the way, we stopped in a place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we were weeks, and weeks, and weeks on the-- on the way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was no food and no supplies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the place that we stopped-- they were a lot of refugees, a lot of people that are-- it was in Russia, on the way to-- to Uzbekistan.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we came to that place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And once a day, they had there-- they were handing out coupons for a meal, but only for a-- for a couple of-- for a short time during the day.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And since they were thousands of people standing in the line, I used to go always with my mother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we were standing in the line.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I said to myself, there is no way we'll ever get anything out of standing here in the line.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So I said to my mother, I am going for a walk.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You stay here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I went for a walk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I surveyed the-- this building.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There was-- it was a small building.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He was sitting in the-- in the window, at a small window.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he was sitting-- it probably wasn't too high.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Because people could reach, and stand in, and you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he was giving out those coupons for a meal.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I surveyed the building.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
